  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/news/\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2-\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da9\u0dd2\u0dba-\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0db8\u0da7-\u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad-\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dcf-\u0d86\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0d9a-\u0d9a\u0dd0\u0db8\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda/101-617035",
  "time_ut": 1658802298,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da9\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc3\u0dbb\u0db8\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad \u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dcf \u0d86\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0d9a \u0d9a\u0dd0\u0db8\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The thief who stole the presidential flag is on security camera",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to police sources, a security camera recorded a private who was among the people who entered the Fort President's House on the 9th, stealing the official flag of the President installed in that house.",
        "The police also mentioned that a person carrying this flag as a saree has been recorded in the CCTV cameras and investigations are being carried out based on the footage.",
        "It is also reported that this flag was installed along with the national flag in the main hall where guests are met.",
        "In addition, some people have stolen a large number of antiques from there, including flag photos, souvenirs, ornaments, flagpoles, historical photos, and many other items, the police said."
      ],
